IF EXIST before running large files and print clear status lines for each step.                                                                                                           config sys config.sys tuning himem.sys dos high umb modest files buffers values compatibility                                                                   CONFIG.SYS tuning                                               Use HIMEM.SYS, DOS=HIGH,UMB, and modest FILES and BUFFERS values for compatibility.                                                                                                             autoexec bat autoexec.bat tuning config.sys loads drivers before sets path variables required tsr tools                                                         AUTOEXEC.BAT tuning                                             CONFIG.SYS loads drivers before AUTOEXEC.BAT; then AUTOEXEC sets PATH, variables, and required TSR tools.                                                                                       cwsdpmi missing protected-mode program fails start copy cwsdpmi.exe beside rerun command                                                                        Missing CWSDPMI                                                 If a protected-mode program fails to start, copy CWSDPMI.EXE beside it and rerun the command.                                                                                                   dosbox mount bundle directory change gpt2 run batch file desired profile                                                                                        DOSBox mount                                                    Mount the bundle directory as C:, change to C:\GPT2, then run the batch file for the desired profile.                                                                                           qemu logs capture compile run copied evidence files before trusting emulator result                                                                   